z0gcode is an independent implementation. It is inspired by terminal coding
agents such as OpenCode (https://github.com/sst/opencode) and Claude Code, but
it does not include their source code; the agent loop, tools, and CLI here are
original.

Bundled third-party content:
- skills/0g/*.md are 0G stack pattern docs adapted from
  0gfoundation/0g-agent-skills (https://github.com/0gfoundation/0g-agent-skills),
  MIT License. They are included to give the agent accurate 0G knowledge.
